Types of records in the battery manufacturing and supply process include parts, manufacturing sites, inventory, production, demand forecasts, quality control records, suppliers, orders, and shipping information.
;
Unique identifiers can help in tracking and managing the records efficiently within the supply chain.

sql:
SELECT site_name, location 
FROM manufacturing_sites
WHERE certifications LIKE '%ISO 9001%';

SELECT part_number, predicted_demand, forecast_model, confidence_level
FROM demand_forecast
WHERE forecast_date BETWEEN '2023-02-01' AND '2023-02-28';

SELECT 
    (SELECT MAX(predicted_demand) FROM demand_forecast WHERE part_number = '0') AS total_predicted_demand,
    (SELECT MAX(quantity) FROM inventory WHERE part_number = '0') AS total_quantity_in_stock;

